{"tid":1378790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首辦否認林鄭因急病辭職","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:12:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"057e7d218ff15392bc249107700a04e8b360416b","tid":1378790,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110102cc86997f24e14437c3d695eb79704055ed","tid":1378790,"uid":258770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"試完水溫發覺唔work"},{"pid":"9128b33f39d96e6db498ecf52ad69a217a878e8b","tid":1378790,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:41:51.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》修訂引發風波，而港澳辦官員今午（29日）會召開記者會講述中央對港問題立場。網上昨日就流傳信息，指特首林鄭月娥患上嚴重健康問題，「無法履行特首職務」離職，稱政務司長張建宗會署任特首6個月，直至新任特首選出，並指消息會於今午3時公布。特首辦主任陳國基回應查詢，指這信息「完全不正確」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190729/s00001/1564330815417/網上流傳林鄭因病辭職-特首辦斥「完全不正確」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190729%2Fs00001%2F1564330815417%2F%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%81%E5%82%B3%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%9B%A0%E7%97%85%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E8%BE%A6%E6%96%A5%E3%80%8C%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA%E3%80%8D&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDLyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=796b008f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190729%2Fs00001%2F1564330815417%2F%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%81%E5%82%B3%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%9B%A0%E7%97%85%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E8%BE%A6%E6%96%A5%E3%80%8C%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA%E3%80%8D&h=a37732e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190729/s00001/1564330815417/網上流傳林鄭因病辭職-特首辦斥「完全不正確」</a>"},{"pid":"e32aa45d7eaa1468b4a6e4bce2b973842d143f7e","tid":1378790,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"辭職根本唔係五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n講黎哂氣"},{"pid":"497540d871debb65411463eda1f98ffcbd48f418","tid":1378790,"uid":146883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:43:18.000Z","msg":"今晚開始不斷有人放風林鄭聽日3點被辭職！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家記住，五大訴求入面係冇林鄭下台既。落台還落台，抗爭還抗爭，係兩回事。<br />\n<br />\n香港的深層次問題，主要係制度問題，更核心既其實係主權問題，而唔單單係領導人的問題。所以無論聽日三點林鄭患淋病又好，生花柳又好，落台又好，繼續「迎難而上」又好，大家緊記要毋忘初衷、堅守原則，堅持到底，就會勝利！<br />\n<br />\n我地係要雙普選！！"},{"pid":"af5bfe6ce62f6c558d11f2587994c291e5511fb5","tid":1378790,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"110102cc86997f24e14437c3d695eb79704055ed","tid":1378790,"uid":258770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"試完水溫發覺唔work"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:43:39.000Z","msg":"成日都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4365c7ca93753702f9d307ae86a4825cbbf5a49","tid":1378790,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:09:00.000Z","msg":"慢性病？"},{"pid":"d136c9154b48bffc14f8a9e0b2115811d7b59d8c","tid":1378790,"uid":61949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"佢遲唔遲係佢嘅事，出唔出黎行係我嘅事。"}]}